      "locked": false,
      "text": "if we want to convert any number to binary-->\n  we have to do its positive numbers 2's compliment.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "if we want to convert any number to binary-->\n  we have to do its positive numbers 2's compliment.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "nJGE5laR01mHurymcZJwa",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 6517.911038940496,
